reviews.text: Stopped in for lunch. The soup of the day was mushroom soup and I have to say it was the best I’ve ever had. Must be the truffle oil drizzled on top. Yum! We also ordered the beef and chicken sliders. They were pretty good. Loved the playlist.

O.k. place for a quick bite & drinks. Very limited choices for food. Quality of food is o.k. prices are reasonable. Drinks are a bit expensive comparatively.  Service is good. Interior of the place is very casual & doesn't fit into hi-end Bar. Worth trying...........😊
Good music and relaxing atmosphere during happy hour. Will definitely go again.
Good enough bar with decent drinks offers. Fills up after work with ex-pat drinkers.

Good service, do happy hour promotions around 19:00 pm (not sure of the exact times or days) food looked great! Beer was fresh on the draft and 2 for 1! Cricket on the TV (no sound) South Africa vs India. Modern and open environment. Visited on a Thursday evening.
